OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThere will be a few early
OL,6,Fshowers, but for most a dry day with
OL,7,Fvariable amounts of cloud and sunny
OL,8,Fintervals. Rather cold with the
OL,9,Foccasionally fresh northwesterly
OL,10,Fbreeze continuing to ease.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThe evening will be dry with
OL,13,Fsome sunshine at first, but gradually
OL,14,Fclouding over from the west. Cloud and
OL,15,Frain will spread east to all parts
OL,16,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
