OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FRain will soon clear east
OL,6,Fthen sunny spells and showers. Drier
OL,7,Ffor a time in the afternoon before
OL,8,Ffurther showers later, heavy at times.
OL,9,FCool and blustery.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FRather
OL,12,Fcold and unsettled Wednesday and
OL,13,FThursday with scattered heavy showers.
OL,14,FChance of overnight frost. Windy
OL,15,Faround the coast on Thursday. Mostly
OL,16,Fdry on Friday but a few early showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
